title: HOUR 2 - Lamar Jackson, John Vilma
itunes:title: HOUR 2 - Lamar Jackson, John Vilma
description:
In hour 2, Colin reacts to Steve Young saying Lamar Jackson has been set up to fail with lack of support to make him a sophisticated passer. John Vilma joins to talk bout Saints rebuilding, Patriots coaching staff issues and more.
